. BUY A FIRE EXTINGUISER
. get a Bentley manual for your bus
. put exhaust back on
. consider putting the Fuel Injection back on
. replace all the fuel lines
. check timing
. replace the .009 distributor (bet you 10 to 1 you've got one) with the
correct vacuum dizzy

good luck

